1
00:01:37,670 --> 00:01:40,539
[Fate Chooses You]

2
00:01:41,320 --> 00:01:43,680
[Episode 29]

3
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:08,419
[Tomb of My Mentor, Duan Xianyin]

4
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:10,770
What's going on?

5
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:13,590
It's Fan.

6
00:02:23,970 --> 00:02:26,850
[Liubo Temple]

7
00:02:27,050 --> 00:02:28,120
-Master!
-Master!

8
00:02:42,710 --> 00:02:43,560
What is this?

9
00:03:05,910 --> 00:03:06,430
Xin Mei.

10
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:10,240
Senior.

11
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:11,950
Senior!

12
00:03:36,030 --> 00:03:36,630
Senior.

13
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:38,290
Are you okay?

14
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:40,560
I'm fine.

15
00:03:44,079 --> 00:03:45,840
Your immortal perception is still here.

16
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:48,500
They didn't extract
your immortal perception.

17
00:04:28,630 --> 00:04:29,910
There's a note for you.

18
00:04:38,870 --> 00:04:40,600
[Come to the pear tree
in Tongyu Alley quickly]

19
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:42,830
Who sent it?

20
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:43,970
I don't know.

21
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,220
While I was out shopping,

22
00:04:45,220 --> 00:04:47,080
someone slipped it into my pouch.

23
00:04:49,780 --> 00:04:51,380
You didn't notice who it was?

24
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,730
Eighty-year-old Suquan wine.

25
00:05:19,390 --> 00:05:21,120
You can't bear to spare me a cup?

26
00:05:24,510 --> 00:05:26,110
Everyone is looking for you,

27
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,800
while you're here, all relaxed.

28
00:05:29,510 --> 00:05:31,390
I would have come even if
they weren't looking for me.

29
00:05:31,390 --> 00:05:33,120
Why do something unnecessary?

30
00:05:35,290 --> 00:05:36,610
What a boast.

31
00:05:39,310 --> 00:05:40,510
You sent me a message.

32
00:05:40,830 --> 00:05:43,230
Weren't you afraid I'd bring people along?

33
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:44,159
You wouldn't.

34
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:45,950
I have investigated you.

35
00:05:45,950 --> 00:05:47,880
You are Fu Tian's direct disciple.

36
00:05:47,960 --> 00:05:49,720
In the 10 years since you joined
the Qinghong Sect,

37
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:50,460
you have become

38
00:05:50,460 --> 00:05:51,790
one of the Eight Vajras.

39
00:05:52,270 --> 00:05:53,970
Previously, at the Yunhan Inn,

40
00:05:53,970 --> 00:05:54,950
you and I joined forces

41
00:05:54,950 --> 00:05:56,480
to kill Dharma King Wenyin.

42
00:05:57,270 --> 00:05:58,190
Back then, I thought you were

43
00:05:58,190 --> 00:05:59,560
just fighting among yourselves.

44
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:01,600
But later at the paper mill,

45
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:03,570
you gave me hints in secret.

46
00:06:04,390 --> 00:06:05,560
I really want to know

47
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:07,510
why you betrayed Fu Tian

48
00:06:08,110 --> 00:06:09,000
to help me.

49
00:06:12,510 --> 00:06:13,720
Why did I help you?

50
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:15,580
Don't you know?

51
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:20,240
Because I like you.

52
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:24,040
You are good-looking,

53
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:26,040
smart, handsome,

54
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:28,070
and very prudish.

55
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:29,830
I...

56
00:06:30,390 --> 00:06:32,270
like men like you.

57
00:06:33,510 --> 00:06:34,310
Why don't you

58
00:06:35,470 --> 00:06:36,830
stop looking for that stubborn girl

59
00:06:36,830 --> 00:06:38,120
from Xin Xie Manor

60
00:06:39,510 --> 00:06:40,920
and be a couple with me

61
00:06:41,310 --> 00:06:41,950
instead?

62
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:44,820
I'm smart, beautiful,

63
00:06:45,070 --> 00:06:46,360
and younger than her.

64
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,190
Moreover,

65
00:06:49,190 --> 00:06:50,920
I am sensible and interesting.

66
00:06:51,380 --> 00:06:53,790
Unlike her, she's so reckless

67
00:06:54,510 --> 00:06:56,040
and causes a lot of trouble.

68
00:06:58,190 --> 00:06:59,040
You like me?

69
00:07:00,830 --> 00:07:02,230
It's love at first sight.

70
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:04,600
No wonder you wrote to Chu Ying,

71
00:07:04,830 --> 00:07:06,600
notifying him to come and save me.

72
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:09,120
You must really love me

73
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:12,070
and have never set me up before.

74
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,430
You really came prepared.

75
00:07:18,630 --> 00:07:19,430
That's right.

76
00:07:19,870 --> 00:07:20,950
I did it.

77
00:07:21,830 --> 00:07:23,360
Since you investigated me,

78
00:07:23,490 --> 00:07:24,450
did you discover

79
00:07:24,750 --> 00:07:26,350
Qinghong Sect's big secret?

80
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:28,270
Secret?

81
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:32,500
Man lives but one life,

82
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:34,810
like a plant lives through one autumn.

83
00:07:34,830 --> 00:07:37,120
Time flies and is ruthless.

84
00:07:37,830 --> 00:07:40,630
Who in this world
doesn't want to be extraordinary

85
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:43,060
and transcend the cycle of life and death?

86
00:07:43,060 --> 00:07:44,990
But without immortal perception,

87
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:47,370
you cannot enter the door of cultivation.

88
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:49,430
Even if you are an emperor or general

89
00:07:49,430 --> 00:07:50,830
holding absolute power,

90
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:52,080
or a wealthy merchant

91
00:07:52,310 --> 00:07:53,440
owning vast riches,

92
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:55,430
as long as you have
no immortal perception,

93
00:07:55,430 --> 00:07:56,630
you are destined to be

94
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:57,950
a mortal in this life.

95
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:02,430
Do you want to know how Fu Tian

96
00:08:02,430 --> 00:08:04,360
took less than a century

97
00:08:04,750 --> 00:08:05,920
to make Qinghong Sect

98
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:07,850
the number one sect in North Xiang?

99
00:08:11,070 --> 00:08:12,310
Because he has a way

100
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:15,040
to let ordinary people without
immortal perception

101
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:16,240
cross the vast chasm,

102
00:08:16,510 --> 00:08:17,910
enter the immortal sect,

103
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:19,560
and become cultivators.

104
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:32,260
Master.

105
00:08:42,390 --> 00:08:43,850
Regardless of your gender

106
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:44,960
or your aptitude,

107
00:08:45,150 --> 00:08:46,480
as long as he is willing,

108
00:08:46,510 --> 00:08:47,840
he can make you break through

109
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:48,910
your limits overnight,

110
00:08:48,910 --> 00:08:51,170
refine your form, and grant you rebirth.

111
00:08:51,670 --> 00:08:53,480
Mortals can become cultivators,

112
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:55,910
and cultivators
can also nourish themselves

113
00:08:55,910 --> 00:08:57,310
to elevate their realms.

114
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,540
Thank you, Master.

115
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:27,910
Aren't you curious

116
00:09:27,910 --> 00:09:29,200
about how he did it?

117
00:09:30,870 --> 00:09:32,390
That's such an important secret.

118
00:09:32,390 --> 00:09:33,050
If I ask you,

119
00:09:33,510 --> 00:09:34,440
will you tell me?

120
00:09:35,530 --> 00:09:37,530
There's nothing that can't be said.

121
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:39,780
I just want you to see it for yourself.

122
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,390
It's a grand matter.

123
00:09:41,870 --> 00:09:43,270
It'd be a pity if you don't

124
00:09:43,630 --> 00:09:44,890
witness it firsthand.

125
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:48,000
You don't have immortal perception either?

126
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:49,800
All members of the Qinghong Sect

127
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:52,260
were transformed from ordinary people.

128
00:09:52,550 --> 00:09:55,150
Cultivators are not trusted.

129
00:09:56,390 --> 00:09:57,000
Why?

130
00:09:57,630 --> 00:09:59,270
Because Fu Tian believes that

131
00:09:59,270 --> 00:10:01,400
only those who have truly been mortals

132
00:10:01,830 --> 00:10:03,960
can genuinely hate the immortal sect.

133
00:10:04,270 --> 00:10:05,750
Only when a moral body

134
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:07,600
crosses the boundary
between immortals and mortals

135
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:09,600
can one be firmly controlled by him.

136
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,730
But you still betrayed him.

137
00:10:13,150 --> 00:10:13,840
Betray him?

138
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:16,600
That sounds too harsh.

139
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:20,200
It seems

140
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:23,000
you still don't understand Qinghong Sect.

141
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,200
Take me, for example.

142
00:10:24,390 --> 00:10:26,840
I grew up in Qinghong Sect
since I was a child.

143
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:28,390
From the first day Fu Tian brought me back

144
00:10:28,390 --> 00:10:30,000
to Qinghong Sect,

145
00:10:30,510 --> 00:10:31,360
he told me

146
00:10:31,890 --> 00:10:33,650
that my parents and clansmen

147
00:10:34,270 --> 00:10:36,330
were all killed by the immortal sect.

148
00:10:36,510 --> 00:10:37,270
I am an orphan

149
00:10:37,270 --> 00:10:38,670
bearing a blood feud.

150
00:10:38,870 --> 00:10:40,270
Haven't you ever doubted

151
00:10:40,510 --> 00:10:42,970
whether what Fu Tian said
was right or wrong?

152
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:46,030
That's why I said you don't understand.

153
00:10:46,030 --> 00:10:47,030
In Qinghong Sect,

154
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:48,440
there are many children

155
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,270
just like me.

156
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:51,670
Everyone is deeply immersed

157
00:10:51,670 --> 00:10:53,150
in the same hatred.

158
00:10:53,690 --> 00:10:55,020
Under such conditions,

159
00:10:55,150 --> 00:10:57,290
discipline is most easily implemented.

160
00:10:57,290 --> 00:10:58,080
Everyone is working hard

161
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,340
towards the same goal,

162
00:10:59,580 --> 00:11:00,190
foolishly

163
00:11:00,670 --> 00:11:02,200
yet firmly.

164
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:05,730
They work their fingers to the bone
every day.

165
00:11:05,870 --> 00:11:08,200
Everyone calls me a demonic enchantress.

166
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,910
I also like this title myself.

167
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:13,460
I even mocked them
for being short-sighted,

168
00:11:13,830 --> 00:11:16,200
unable to discern
good from evil in this world,

169
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:18,730
or notice the hypocrisy
of the immortal sect.

170
00:11:20,390 --> 00:11:21,440
Until one day,

171
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:22,860
I found out that

172
00:11:23,310 --> 00:11:26,510
Qinghong Sect was sending medicine
to the immortal sect.

173
00:11:27,910 --> 00:11:28,770
What medicine?

174
00:11:32,750 --> 00:11:34,280
You must have seen this too.

175
00:11:36,250 --> 00:11:39,310
The Yangyuan Pill
commonly eaten by the immortal sect?

176
00:11:41,270 --> 00:11:42,070
That's right.

177
00:11:42,630 --> 00:11:44,150
They often use this medicine

178
00:11:44,150 --> 00:11:46,750
to increase their skills,
repair their Qihai,

179
00:11:46,790 --> 00:11:48,250
and nourish their bodies.

180
00:11:56,910 --> 00:11:58,040
Why do you have this?

181
00:11:58,390 --> 00:11:59,000
I got this

182
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:00,330
from the Bishui Branch.

183
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:01,840
At that time, the Branch Master

184
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:03,240
drank this golden liquid

185
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:04,750
and improved his skills greatly.

186
00:12:04,750 --> 00:12:06,270
He even advanced on the spot.

187
00:12:06,270 --> 00:12:07,550
I once asked Su Taiyi

188
00:12:07,830 --> 00:12:09,240
about the origin of this golden liquid.

189
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:10,790
He said it had similar ingredients

190
00:12:10,790 --> 00:12:11,990
to the Yangyuan Pill.

191
00:12:12,750 --> 00:12:13,670
Not similar.

192
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:16,280
They are exactly the same thing.

193
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:17,660
This golden liquid

194
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:19,240
is extracted from the immortal perception

195
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:20,170
of cultivators.

196
00:12:20,670 --> 00:12:22,440
The higher the cultivator's realm,

197
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:23,720
the purer the extracted golden liquid,

198
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:24,670
and the greater

199
00:12:25,150 --> 00:12:26,480
the energy it provides.

200
00:12:26,670 --> 00:12:27,730
The Yangyuan Pills

201
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:29,870
are simply pills made from very diluted

202
00:12:29,870 --> 00:12:31,000
golden liquid.

203
00:12:31,670 --> 00:12:32,470
So,

204
00:12:33,030 --> 00:12:33,830
Qinghong Sect

205
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:35,480
is extracting golden liquid

206
00:12:35,750 --> 00:12:37,240
from the immortal perception
of cultivators.

207
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:38,200
A portion of it

208
00:12:38,630 --> 00:12:41,080
is used to transform
mortals into cultivators,

209
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:42,390
while the other portion

210
00:12:42,390 --> 00:12:43,870
is made into Yangyuan Pills

211
00:12:43,870 --> 00:12:45,670
and resold to the immortal sect.

212
00:12:46,870 --> 00:12:48,400
Sounds ridiculous, right?

213
00:12:49,170 --> 00:12:51,170
Claiming to hate the immortal sect,

214
00:12:51,550 --> 00:12:53,200
but wanting to become the immortal sect

215
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:54,080
and rely on it.

216
00:12:54,870 --> 00:12:56,080
Many of my friends

217
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:57,630
died while fighting

218
00:12:57,630 --> 00:12:58,900
against the immortal sect.

219
00:12:58,900 --> 00:13:00,020
If Qinghong Sect

220
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:02,200
is a vassal of the immortal sect...

221
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:03,630
If everything is fake,

222
00:13:04,200 --> 00:13:06,510
then what about the people who died?

223
00:13:09,300 --> 00:13:10,610
Lord Baori of our sect

224
00:13:10,920 --> 00:13:13,980
is someone sent by
the immortal sect of Central Plains.

225
00:13:16,510 --> 00:13:17,240
Lu Qianqiao.

226
00:13:19,030 --> 00:13:20,430
I know you are a War Demon.

227
00:13:20,870 --> 00:13:22,270
After the Battle of Pinghu,

228
00:13:22,270 --> 00:13:23,870
the War Demons disappeared.

229
00:13:24,180 --> 00:13:25,780
You are a loner now.

230
00:13:26,750 --> 00:13:28,270
You don't belong to the War Demons,

231
00:13:28,270 --> 00:13:29,270
the Human Race,

232
00:13:29,600 --> 00:13:31,660
and certainly not the immortal sect.

233
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:33,630
These years,

234
00:13:34,500 --> 00:13:35,360
I suppose your life

235
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:36,760
hasn't been easy either.

236
00:13:37,390 --> 00:13:38,900
You should understand the feeling

237
00:13:38,900 --> 00:13:40,000
of working hard for a goal

238
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:41,000
since childhood,

239
00:13:41,670 --> 00:13:42,530
only to find out

240
00:13:43,330 --> 00:13:44,330
in the end that

241
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:45,840
everything is a scam.

242
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:48,600
I, Zuo Yingying, considered myself smart,

243
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:49,840
but I was deceived,

244
00:13:50,240 --> 00:13:50,750
lied to,

245
00:13:51,390 --> 00:13:52,990
and played for a fool by them.

246
00:13:54,050 --> 00:13:54,850
Why?

247
00:13:57,910 --> 00:13:59,110
What do you want to do?

248
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:00,360
I want to try.

249
00:14:01,630 --> 00:14:02,200
Try what?

250
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:03,720
I want to try

251
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:06,510
to kill Fu Tian,

252
00:14:07,440 --> 00:14:08,970
destroy the Qinghong Sect,

253
00:14:09,390 --> 00:14:11,520
and break this cage that imprisons me.

254
00:14:14,790 --> 00:14:15,520
How about it?

255
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:18,130
Shall we cooperate?

256
00:14:19,070 --> 00:14:21,000
It won't be the first time, anyway.

257
00:14:24,730 --> 00:14:27,990
[Phoenix City]

258
00:14:24,870 --> 00:14:27,350
Phoenix City is 1 of the 3 towns
in the Western Regions.

259
00:14:27,350 --> 00:14:29,480
It connects Mohe to the east,
Banchi to the west,

260
00:14:29,480 --> 00:14:30,750
and Xiongshan to the south.

261
00:14:30,750 --> 00:14:31,480
Since ancient times,

262
00:14:31,480 --> 00:14:33,670
it has been a prosperous place for trade.

263
00:14:33,670 --> 00:14:34,870
After the Battle of Pinghu,

264
00:14:34,870 --> 00:14:35,550
the Emperor of the Human Race

265
00:14:35,550 --> 00:14:37,080
took the opportunity
to recover Phoenix City

266
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:39,080
and sent soldiers to garrison here.

267
00:14:39,150 --> 00:14:40,200
Nominally, Phoenix City

268
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:41,720
is under the jurisdiction
of the Central Plains.

269
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:42,510
But in fact,

270
00:14:43,010 --> 00:14:44,480
the Qinghong Sect has infiltrated

271
00:14:44,480 --> 00:14:45,480
every corner.

272
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:47,360
Once the people of the Wushuang Society
and the immortal sect

273
00:14:47,360 --> 00:14:48,560
step into this place,

274
00:14:48,850 --> 00:14:49,670
they will be within

275
00:14:49,670 --> 00:14:50,720
our line of sight.

276
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:53,000
Then why did you let them

277
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:54,890
burn down the Sihe Library?

278
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:56,960
Because it's not important.

279
00:14:56,970 --> 00:14:57,720
The people of the Wushuang Society

280
00:14:57,720 --> 00:14:59,240
care about the Unparalleled Secret Magic.

281
00:14:59,240 --> 00:15:01,240
But the Qinghong Sect is different.

282
00:15:01,270 --> 00:15:03,030
Although we have no immortal perception,

283
00:15:03,030 --> 00:15:05,290
we also practice the art of cultivation.

284
00:15:06,270 --> 00:15:08,330
The Qinghong Sect members
practice with secret methods,

285
00:15:08,330 --> 00:15:09,600
vainly attempting to use mortal bodies

286
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:10,910
to become immortals and saints.

287
00:15:10,910 --> 00:15:12,240
From this perspective,

288
00:15:12,240 --> 00:15:14,440
the Wushuang Society is also our enemy.

289
00:15:19,270 --> 00:15:21,030
Then why did you collect ancient books

290
00:15:21,030 --> 00:15:22,560
and build the Sihe Library?

291
00:15:23,390 --> 00:15:24,650
Because that's a trap.

292
00:15:25,080 --> 00:15:26,960
As long as the Sihe Library is there,

293
00:15:26,960 --> 00:15:28,220
groups of people from the Wushuang Society

294
00:15:28,220 --> 00:15:29,950
will come here.

295
00:15:30,870 --> 00:15:31,870
As long as they come,

296
00:15:31,870 --> 00:15:33,960
the immortal sect members will come after.

297
00:15:33,960 --> 00:15:35,550
There is a saying in the Central Plains:

298
00:15:35,550 --> 00:15:37,840
the mantis stalks the cicada,
unaware of the oriole behind.

299
00:15:37,840 --> 00:15:38,900
That's exactly it.

300
00:15:41,840 --> 00:15:42,790
After the immortal sect members

301
00:15:42,790 --> 00:15:44,750
and your group
wounded each other in battle,

302
00:15:44,750 --> 00:15:46,790
our people took the opportunity to act.

303
00:15:46,790 --> 00:15:47,600
Now, most of them

304
00:15:47,600 --> 00:15:49,660
are locked in the dungeon of our sect,

305
00:15:49,750 --> 00:15:50,790
including Xin Mei,

306
00:15:50,790 --> 00:15:51,750
her junior,

307
00:15:52,240 --> 00:15:53,910
and your swordsman friend.

308
00:15:55,790 --> 00:15:57,520
Lord of Rust-Sword isn't dead?

309
00:15:58,910 --> 00:15:59,630
Not at all.

310
00:16:00,550 --> 00:16:01,480
He's very lucky.

311
00:16:03,270 --> 00:16:04,320
Can you help me

312
00:16:04,550 --> 00:16:05,480
save them?

313
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:08,830
Master is certain
you'd go back to save them,

314
00:16:08,830 --> 00:16:10,030
and has set up an inescapable trap

315
00:16:10,030 --> 00:16:10,630
for you.

316
00:16:11,450 --> 00:16:12,720
He also sent his Right Protector,

317
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:14,650
Lord Tiling, to guard the dungeon.

318
00:16:14,960 --> 00:16:16,960
He's a cultivator in the Void Stage.

319
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:18,320
With such a huge risk,

320
00:16:18,390 --> 00:16:19,590
why should I help you?

321
00:16:20,320 --> 00:16:22,480
I will help you kill Fu Tian,

322
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:24,030
destroy the Qinghong Sect,

323
00:16:24,030 --> 00:16:26,030
and break the cage imprisoning you.

324
00:16:26,550 --> 00:16:27,390
By yourself?

325
00:16:28,720 --> 00:16:29,650
What do you mean?

326
00:16:30,080 --> 00:16:31,080
Am I not also here?

327
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:34,080
What's your plan?

328
00:16:35,720 --> 00:16:36,550
Three days later,

329
00:16:36,550 --> 00:16:39,080
Qinghong Sect will be holding
the ritual assembly.

330
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:41,000
I heard Fu Tian will recruit disciples

331
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:42,480
into the sect at the assembly.

332
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:43,480
According to you,

333
00:16:43,870 --> 00:16:45,690
he'll use his secret arts
to help ordinary mortals

334
00:16:45,690 --> 00:16:46,980
cross the boundary
between mortals and immortals

335
00:16:46,980 --> 00:16:49,440
and step into
the Cultivation Realm, right?

336
00:16:50,650 --> 00:16:53,170
I will kill him in public that day.

337
00:17:01,700 --> 00:17:02,290
Come in.

338
00:18:13,880 --> 00:18:14,440
How is it?

339
00:18:17,350 --> 00:18:18,680
What about you, Senior?

340
00:18:22,450 --> 00:18:23,590
They used the Nine Breaths Technique

341
00:18:23,590 --> 00:18:25,960
to seal off our acupoints
and nine apertures.

342
00:18:25,960 --> 00:18:26,590
They severed our connection

343
00:18:26,590 --> 00:18:29,050
to the spiritual energy
of heaven and earth.

344
00:18:29,180 --> 00:18:30,310
Even if I forcefully activate

345
00:18:30,310 --> 00:18:32,030
the spiritual energy in my body,

346
00:18:32,030 --> 00:18:34,000
it will soon be suppressed and sealed.

347
00:18:34,000 --> 00:18:35,730
I can't break through it at all.

348
00:18:44,720 --> 00:18:45,270
Break!

349
00:18:46,760 --> 00:18:47,410
Break!

350
00:18:49,000 --> 00:18:49,480
Break!

351
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:51,480
Break!

352
00:18:52,350 --> 00:18:52,880
Break!

353
00:18:58,110 --> 00:18:59,030
Even if you trigger

354
00:18:59,030 --> 00:19:00,750
all the power in the formation,

355
00:19:00,750 --> 00:19:02,480
you still can't break the seal.

356
00:19:02,510 --> 00:19:03,400
And it might cause

357
00:19:03,400 --> 00:19:04,480
the two forces to clash,

358
00:19:04,480 --> 00:19:05,590
making it backfire on you

359
00:19:05,590 --> 00:19:06,850
and cost you your life.

360
00:19:07,070 --> 00:19:08,270
Then what do we do now?

361
00:19:08,310 --> 00:19:09,440
Just wait for death?

362
00:19:10,480 --> 00:19:11,480
Watch your tone.

363
00:19:12,110 --> 00:19:13,030
If I had known,

364
00:19:13,650 --> 00:19:14,590
I would have learned more from my father

365
00:19:14,590 --> 00:19:16,590
about the formation to break seals.

366
00:19:16,750 --> 00:19:18,240
Then we wouldn't be

367
00:19:18,640 --> 00:19:20,400
sitting ducks like this today.

368
00:19:30,510 --> 00:19:31,170
How are you?

369
00:19:33,440 --> 00:19:34,960
If my Divine Sword were here,

370
00:19:34,960 --> 00:19:35,880
I'd have been able to

371
00:19:35,880 --> 00:19:37,410
gather qi with my sword will

372
00:19:37,480 --> 00:19:38,880
and break this damn seal.

373
00:19:39,790 --> 00:19:41,050
If my father were here,

374
00:19:41,870 --> 00:19:43,590
the people outside would be dead by now.

375
00:19:43,590 --> 00:19:44,550
How pointless.

376
00:20:05,550 --> 00:20:08,000
Slower. I told you to be slower.

377
00:20:08,030 --> 00:20:09,110
You're still too fast.

378
00:20:09,110 --> 00:20:10,550
You need to be slower.

379
00:20:10,680 --> 00:20:11,920
Even slower?

380
00:20:21,760 --> 00:20:23,610
Can such a weak move

381
00:20:23,960 --> 00:20:24,960
even hit anyone?

382
00:20:28,590 --> 00:20:29,660
The path of cultivation

383
00:20:29,660 --> 00:20:32,240
is about understanding the Dao
and practicing methods,

384
00:20:32,240 --> 00:20:34,920
gathering qi and condensing power
to defeat the enemy.

385
00:20:34,920 --> 00:20:36,920
The key is that you must understand

386
00:20:37,070 --> 00:20:38,480
what Dao you cultivate,

387
00:20:38,590 --> 00:20:39,880
what method you practice,

388
00:20:39,880 --> 00:20:40,940
what qi you gather,

389
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:43,000
and what power you utilize.

390
00:20:44,680 --> 00:20:45,870
Master, you once said that

391
00:20:45,870 --> 00:20:46,890
we righteous cultivators

392
00:20:46,890 --> 00:20:48,650
cultivate the Dao of Heaven,

393
00:20:48,830 --> 00:20:51,200
gather the qi of the five elements,
and utilize pure spiritual power.

394
00:20:51,200 --> 00:20:52,270
The path of cultivation

395
00:20:52,270 --> 00:20:54,200
is a path of defying heaven
to fight for life.

396
00:20:54,200 --> 00:20:56,550
Remember not to just memorize by rote.

397
00:20:57,680 --> 00:20:59,070
Please enlighten me, Master.

398
00:20:59,070 --> 00:21:00,310
As for the Dao of Heaven,

399
00:21:00,310 --> 00:21:01,270
I will properly explain them to you

400
00:21:01,270 --> 00:21:02,640
another day.

401
00:21:03,310 --> 00:21:05,350
Today, I'll first tell you about

402
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:07,550
the qi of the five elements.

403
00:21:08,160 --> 00:21:11,490
The qi of the five elements
is divided into clear and turbid.

404
00:21:11,790 --> 00:21:14,160
Clear qi is pure and immaculate.

405
00:21:14,200 --> 00:21:15,680
The more you absorb,

406
00:21:15,700 --> 00:21:16,980
the stronger the spiritual power

407
00:21:16,980 --> 00:21:18,220
you condense.

408
00:21:19,590 --> 00:21:20,590
And the turbid qi?

409
00:21:20,720 --> 00:21:23,510
Turbid qi is chaotic and uncontrollable.

410
00:21:23,720 --> 00:21:25,810
If you accidentally
inhale the slightest bit,

411
00:21:25,810 --> 00:21:27,440
it will corrode your immortal perception,

412
00:21:27,440 --> 00:21:29,420
making it impossible for your cultivation

413
00:21:29,420 --> 00:21:30,770
to improve any further.

414
00:21:31,240 --> 00:21:32,430
Is there no one in this world

415
00:21:32,430 --> 00:21:34,290
who mainly cultivates turbid qi?

416
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:36,000
There are.
Heretical cultivator, for example.

417
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:37,160
Of course, they have almost been wiped out

418
00:21:37,160 --> 00:21:38,830
by me.

419
00:21:41,160 --> 00:21:42,490
But I don't understand.

420
00:21:42,830 --> 00:21:44,980
Both types belong
to the qi of the five elements.

421
00:21:44,980 --> 00:21:46,720
Why are those
who mainly cultivate turbid qi

422
00:21:46,720 --> 00:21:48,060
called heretical cultivators?

423
00:21:48,060 --> 00:21:50,310
That's because
they are eager for quick success

424
00:21:50,310 --> 00:21:51,220
and have improper intentions.

425
00:21:51,220 --> 00:21:53,150
It has nothing to do with turbid qi.

426
00:21:54,640 --> 00:21:55,680
So does that mean

427
00:21:55,880 --> 00:21:57,160
turbid qi can also

428
00:21:57,160 --> 00:21:58,700
condense into powerful spiritual energy?

429
00:21:58,700 --> 00:22:00,920
Yin alone cannot exist;
Yang alone cannot grow.

430
00:22:00,920 --> 00:22:03,070
In theory, this is true.

431
00:22:03,200 --> 00:22:04,510
But no one in this world

432
00:22:04,510 --> 00:22:05,750
can successfully cultivate turbid qi,

433
00:22:05,750 --> 00:22:07,950
nor can anyone use it to prove their Dao.

434
00:22:09,720 --> 00:22:10,480
My disciple,

435
00:22:10,830 --> 00:22:12,070
remember this.

436
00:22:13,400 --> 00:22:15,440
All things share the same source.

437
00:22:15,880 --> 00:22:18,340
Heaven and earth are originally connected.

438
00:22:18,350 --> 00:22:20,160
Absorbing clear qi is the foundation.

439
00:22:20,160 --> 00:22:22,510
The state of mind has no beginning or end.

440
00:22:23,350 --> 00:22:25,400
Clouds roll and unroll.

441
00:22:25,480 --> 00:22:27,340
Wind comes and goes in emptiness.

442
00:22:27,680 --> 00:22:29,640
Firmly guard the true original intent.

443
00:22:29,640 --> 00:22:31,720
Do not let the turbid become a flood.

444
00:22:57,590 --> 00:22:59,590
Senior, did you think of something?

445
00:23:00,930 --> 00:23:01,830
The Nine Breaths Technique

446
00:23:01,830 --> 00:23:03,290
has used the Five Elements

447
00:23:03,400 --> 00:23:04,110
to sever our connection

448
00:23:04,110 --> 00:23:05,790
with heaven and earth's spiritual power.

449
00:23:05,790 --> 00:23:06,310
But,

450
00:23:07,110 --> 00:23:08,030
it has only sealed

451
00:23:08,030 --> 00:23:10,030
our spiritual energy from clear qi.

452
00:23:15,240 --> 00:23:16,300
Isn't that enough?

453
00:23:19,680 --> 00:23:20,970
Under the vast Dao of Heaven,

454
00:23:20,970 --> 00:23:22,200
it's not like we can only gather

455
00:23:22,200 --> 00:23:23,400
clear qi into energy.

456
00:23:23,830 --> 00:23:25,240
What if I do the opposite?

457
00:23:25,880 --> 00:23:26,750
You mean,

458
00:23:27,160 --> 00:23:28,290
we can turn turbid qi

459
00:23:28,780 --> 00:23:29,980
into energy instead?

460
00:23:30,160 --> 00:23:30,690
Exactly.

461
00:23:31,480 --> 00:23:32,000
No.

462
00:23:34,440 --> 00:23:36,240
Do you have a better idea, Sheng?

463
00:23:37,520 --> 00:23:38,960
Then let me take the risk.

464
00:23:39,510 --> 00:23:40,400
Among us,

465
00:23:41,200 --> 00:23:42,030
I’m the only one

466
00:23:42,030 --> 00:23:43,490
at the Nascent Soul Stage.

467
00:23:43,790 --> 00:23:44,310
So,

468
00:23:44,920 --> 00:23:46,480
if we want to expel the clear
and gather the turbid,

469
00:23:46,480 --> 00:23:47,880
I have the highest chance

470
00:23:48,070 --> 00:23:49,270
of breaking the seal.

471
00:23:50,410 --> 00:23:51,940
What are you arguing about?

472
00:23:52,880 --> 00:23:54,480
When heaven and earth were created,

473
00:23:54,480 --> 00:23:55,880
mountains stood, and rivers flowed.

474
00:23:55,880 --> 00:23:57,870
The two qis operated wonderfully within,

475
00:23:57,870 --> 00:23:59,470
parallel without conflict.

476
00:23:59,590 --> 00:24:01,720
The light and clear yang qi
rose to become heaven,

477
00:24:01,720 --> 00:24:03,680
while the heavy and turbid yin qi
sank to become earth.

478
00:24:03,680 --> 00:24:05,480
Where qi gathers in abundance,
conception occurs.

479
00:24:05,480 --> 00:24:07,270
Where qi comes alive and stirs,
nurturing begins.

480
00:24:07,270 --> 00:24:08,750
Where qi fuses and binds,
the fetus takes form.

481
00:24:08,750 --> 00:24:11,240
Where qi briefly comes to rest,
breath is drawn.

482
00:24:11,240 --> 00:24:12,160
Yin and yang

483
00:24:12,510 --> 00:24:13,970
represent death and life,

484
00:24:14,070 --> 00:24:15,070
clear and turbid.

485
00:24:15,510 --> 00:24:16,790
They complement each other

486
00:24:16,790 --> 00:24:18,000
and are born together.

487
00:24:18,000 --> 00:24:19,310
But during cultivation,

488
00:24:19,310 --> 00:24:20,720
one must reject the turbid
and accept the clear

489
00:24:20,720 --> 00:24:22,050
to enrich their origin,

490
00:24:22,270 --> 00:24:23,310
fuel the cycle,

491
00:24:23,830 --> 00:24:25,490
and generate endless energy.

492
00:24:26,680 --> 00:24:27,240
So,

493
00:24:27,790 --> 00:24:28,830
in simple terms,

494
00:24:29,000 --> 00:24:30,130
what does that mean?

495
00:24:30,510 --> 00:24:31,590
Ignorant.

496
00:24:32,350 --> 00:24:33,160
Xin Mei is planning

497
00:24:33,160 --> 00:24:34,220
to do the opposite.

498
00:24:34,640 --> 00:24:36,360
She plans to absorb the turbid qi here,

499
00:24:36,360 --> 00:24:37,880
turn it into power,

500
00:24:38,510 --> 00:24:40,310
break the seal from the outside,

501
00:24:40,880 --> 00:24:41,790
and lift the Nine Breaths Technique

502
00:24:41,790 --> 00:24:43,190
that is trapping us here.

503
00:24:44,640 --> 00:24:45,970
Isn't that a good thing?

504
00:24:47,310 --> 00:24:49,840
But turbid qi is chaotic
and uncontrollable.

505
00:24:50,070 --> 00:24:51,400
One mistake, and it will

506
00:24:51,440 --> 00:24:52,830
corrode her immortal perception,

507
00:24:52,830 --> 00:24:56,030
making it impossible for her
to improve her cultivation.

508
00:24:56,270 --> 00:24:57,030
Senior.

509
00:24:57,640 --> 00:24:58,480
Let me try.

510
00:25:00,640 --> 00:25:01,270
Sheng.

511
00:25:02,160 --> 00:25:03,000
I am already

512
00:25:03,000 --> 00:25:04,530
a Nascent Soul cultivator.

513
00:25:05,050 --> 00:25:06,770
So many people can never reach

514
00:25:07,200 --> 00:25:09,210
the Nascent Soul stage in their lifetime.

515
00:25:09,210 --> 00:25:10,670
I am already very content.

516
00:25:13,720 --> 00:25:15,830
The Qinghong Sect
has malicious intentions.

517
00:25:15,830 --> 00:25:17,490
Not only did they imprison us,

518
00:25:17,680 --> 00:25:20,050
but they also had ulterior
motives for Lu Qianqiao.

519
00:25:20,050 --> 00:25:20,880
Our lives may be in danger

520
00:25:20,880 --> 00:25:21,920
at any moment.

521
00:25:22,200 --> 00:25:24,060
We must escape from here quickly.

522
00:25:44,790 --> 00:25:47,440
That person seems to be
from the Wang family of Jinqiu.

523
00:25:47,440 --> 00:25:48,680
Why is he here?

524
00:25:53,240 --> 00:25:54,430
You are good at formations.

525
00:25:54,430 --> 00:25:55,960
Can you set one up to help me?

526
00:25:57,430 --> 00:25:57,830
No.

527
00:25:58,510 --> 00:26:00,040
This method is too harmful.

528
00:26:00,090 --> 00:26:01,750
I can't set you up for failure.

529
00:26:01,920 --> 00:26:02,610
Tell me.

530
00:26:05,480 --> 00:26:06,790
The conditions to activate this formation

531
00:26:06,790 --> 00:26:08,050
are extremely strict.

532
00:26:08,110 --> 00:26:09,310
I have never tried it.

533
00:26:09,480 --> 00:26:10,110
I don't even know

534
00:26:10,110 --> 00:26:11,040
if I can succeed.

535
00:26:11,550 --> 00:26:12,250
First,

536
00:26:12,590 --> 00:26:13,640
we need to gather the impure variations

537
00:26:13,640 --> 00:26:14,770
of the five elements

538
00:26:14,880 --> 00:26:16,080
and turbid qi itself.

539
00:26:35,990 --> 00:26:38,200
Foul stagnant water can be impure water.

540
00:26:38,200 --> 00:26:40,730
Filthy soil from a prison
can be impure earth.

541
00:26:41,550 --> 00:26:43,070
Then we still need impure metal,

542
00:26:43,070 --> 00:26:43,800
impure wood,

543
00:26:43,910 --> 00:26:44,840
and impure fire.

544
00:26:46,200 --> 00:26:47,000
Does qi count?

545
00:26:47,830 --> 00:26:48,310
Yes.

546
00:26:49,070 --> 00:26:50,130
Will sword qi work?

547
00:26:50,960 --> 00:26:52,360
Sword qi is indeed metal,

548
00:26:52,680 --> 00:26:54,210
but it must be impure metal.

549
00:26:54,350 --> 00:26:55,550
What is impure metal?

550
00:26:55,750 --> 00:26:56,880
Generally speaking,

551
00:26:56,880 --> 00:26:58,440
anything tainted with resentment,

552
00:26:58,440 --> 00:26:58,880
anger,

553
00:26:59,310 --> 00:26:59,960
decay,

554
00:27:00,510 --> 00:27:02,070
sorrow, disaster,

555
00:27:02,400 --> 00:27:06,200
obscenity, cruelty, pain, disease,

556
00:27:06,440 --> 00:27:08,170
murderous intent, and the like

557
00:27:08,200 --> 00:27:09,730
can be called impure metal.

558
00:27:11,160 --> 00:27:12,350
Are impure wood and impure fire

559
00:27:12,350 --> 00:27:13,270
the same?

560
00:27:14,510 --> 00:27:15,160
Yes.

561
00:27:15,830 --> 00:27:17,270
I can summon the Divine Sword

562
00:27:17,270 --> 00:27:18,680
to arouse
the murderous intent in my heart.

563
00:27:18,680 --> 00:27:20,610
A murderous blade would be impure.

564
00:27:20,680 --> 00:27:21,940
I will handle the fire.

565
00:27:22,030 --> 00:27:24,230
A resentful fire is considered impure.

566
00:27:24,310 --> 00:27:25,550
Then I will handle the wood.

567
00:27:25,550 --> 00:27:27,680
A decaying dead wood is considered impure.

568
00:27:27,680 --> 00:27:28,240
Okay.

569
00:27:28,830 --> 00:27:30,030
Then we have them all.

570
00:27:39,130 --> 00:27:40,410
Master has arrived!

571
00:27:43,920 --> 00:27:45,790
Welcome, Master.

572
00:28:54,750 --> 00:28:57,990
♪ Pointing to the sky,
questioning the moon ♪

573
00:28:58,010 --> 00:29:01,270
♪ I'd rather be a wandering immortal
in the mortal world ♪

574
00:29:01,540 --> 00:29:04,770
♪ And experience it all for myself ♪

575
00:29:04,910 --> 00:29:08,260
♪ Right and wrong, justice and evil ♪

576
00:29:08,320 --> 00:29:11,500
♪ In all the world,
I choose first the people ♪

577
00:29:08,880 --> 00:29:10,200
The murderous blade you gathered

578
00:29:10,200 --> 00:29:10,860
is too weak.

579
00:29:11,310 --> 00:29:12,110
I can't form the formation this way.

580
00:29:12,110 --> 00:29:14,960
♪ How could the powerful lie drunk
in golden halls ♪

581
00:29:15,250 --> 00:29:18,250
♪ Illusions of heaven
and memory entwined ♪

582
00:29:18,590 --> 00:29:20,500
♪ I will still break
into this mortal realm ♪

583
00:29:20,750 --> 00:29:22,960
♪ To demand a rightful ending ♪

584
00:29:33,310 --> 00:29:35,030
Greetings, Master.

585
00:29:35,680 --> 00:29:38,830
May the Sect Leader
shine as eternal as the sun and moon.

586
00:29:39,310 --> 00:29:42,680
May the Sect Leader
share the glory of heaven and earth.

587
00:29:43,480 --> 00:29:44,270
Today

588
00:29:44,960 --> 00:29:46,890
is the birthday of the Phoenix God,

589
00:29:47,160 --> 00:29:50,240
and also an auspicious day

590
00:29:50,750 --> 00:29:52,880
when the Phoenix God descends to bless

591
00:29:53,070 --> 00:29:54,270
all living beings.

592
00:29:54,880 --> 00:29:57,640
The Phoenix God traverses heaven and earth

593
00:29:58,000 --> 00:29:59,260
as the Lord of all gods.

594
00:29:59,790 --> 00:30:02,590
We should follow the Phoenix God

595
00:30:03,310 --> 00:30:06,510
to eradicate all evil in the world,

596
00:30:07,310 --> 00:30:09,270
achieve unprecedented feats,

597
00:30:09,720 --> 00:30:11,550
be granted righteous status,

598
00:30:11,920 --> 00:30:15,630
and ascend to heaven
to live forever with the Dao.

599
00:30:16,440 --> 00:30:19,830
Dao of Heaven, may we never age.

600
00:30:20,400 --> 00:30:24,000
Live as long as the earth,
and ascend to heaven soon.

601
00:30:24,350 --> 00:30:27,550
May my life be prolonged
to live forever with the Dao.

602
00:30:27,880 --> 00:30:31,440
May my life be prolonged
to live forever with the Dao.

603
00:30:53,750 --> 00:30:54,810
Greetings, Vajra.

604
00:30:55,610 --> 00:30:57,880
Today, the sect is holding
a blessing ceremony.

605
00:30:57,880 --> 00:31:00,160
To prevent scoundrels from
the immortal sect from causing trouble,

606
00:31:00,160 --> 00:31:01,560
you must be on full alert.

607
00:31:01,580 --> 00:31:02,510
Do not slack off.

608
00:31:03,000 --> 00:31:03,550
Yes.

609
00:32:28,790 --> 00:32:29,590
Are you ready?

610
00:32:30,750 --> 00:32:32,470
I am going to start the formation.

611
00:32:32,470 --> 00:32:33,130
Bring it on.

612
00:32:34,970 --> 00:32:36,790
The Five Elements are born,
each with its own nature.

613
00:32:36,790 --> 00:32:38,750
Their essences miraculously
combine and condense.

614
00:32:38,750 --> 00:32:40,750
The interaction of two energies
creates everything.

615
00:32:40,750 --> 00:32:42,450
All things multiply and change endlessly.

616
00:32:42,450 --> 00:32:43,050
Activate!

617
00:33:03,030 --> 00:33:05,880
Who is fortunate enough
to join the sect today?

618
00:33:09,480 --> 00:33:10,740
Where is Wang Yanqing?

619
00:33:16,510 --> 00:33:18,510
Devout follower Wang Yanqing is here.

620
00:33:18,510 --> 00:33:21,440
Congratulations on the birthday
of the Phoenix God.

621
00:33:21,540 --> 00:33:22,400
I congratulate

622
00:33:23,110 --> 00:33:24,640
our God and the Sect Master.

623
00:33:24,920 --> 00:33:26,180
May you be as enduring as the moon,

624
00:33:26,180 --> 00:33:27,580
and as radiant as the sun.

625
00:33:29,440 --> 00:33:30,900
Report to the Phoenix God,

626
00:33:31,550 --> 00:33:33,080
and tell everyone present,

627
00:33:33,560 --> 00:33:34,400
who you are.

628
00:33:35,510 --> 00:33:37,570
I come from the Wang family of Jinqiu.

629
00:33:38,070 --> 00:33:39,590
I'm the direct heir of the Wang family.

630
00:33:39,590 --> 00:33:40,990
The Wang family of Jinqiu

631
00:33:41,000 --> 00:33:42,830
has produced cultivators in the past,

632
00:33:42,830 --> 00:33:45,400
so it can be considered
a family of cultivators.

633
00:33:45,400 --> 00:33:46,400
As far as I know,

634
00:33:46,790 --> 00:33:49,000
your family has always been
subordinate to the immortal sect,

635
00:33:49,000 --> 00:33:50,000
serving them.

636
00:33:50,480 --> 00:33:51,140
So why do you

637
00:33:52,160 --> 00:33:54,360
want to join our Qinghong Holy Sect now?

638
00:33:54,960 --> 00:33:56,820
You may not know this, Venerable.

639
00:33:57,420 --> 00:33:58,280
Over the years,

640
00:33:58,880 --> 00:34:00,210
our Wang family may seem

641
00:34:00,640 --> 00:34:02,500
to be driven by the immortal sect,

642
00:34:02,590 --> 00:34:03,450
but in reality,

643
00:34:04,210 --> 00:34:05,200
we are forced to serve

644
00:34:05,200 --> 00:34:06,600
by their despotic power.

645
00:34:06,850 --> 00:34:08,449
They are cruel and ruthless,

646
00:34:08,480 --> 00:34:10,409
and do not treat us as humans at all.

647
00:34:10,570 --> 00:34:12,830
They take whatever
they want from my family,

648
00:34:12,830 --> 00:34:14,550
and the slightest hesitation from us

649
00:34:14,550 --> 00:34:16,150
would bring fatal disaster.

650
00:34:17,590 --> 00:34:18,590
Who in your family

651
00:34:18,710 --> 00:34:20,770
has been harmed by the immortal sect?

652
00:34:21,710 --> 00:34:22,510
My father

653
00:34:23,360 --> 00:34:24,360
and elder brother

654
00:34:25,230 --> 00:34:27,360
were both killed by the immortal sect.

655
00:34:27,489 --> 00:34:28,710
Our Wang family has been driven

656
00:34:28,710 --> 00:34:30,570
to a dead end by the immortal sect.

657
00:34:30,750 --> 00:34:31,510
The reason I could

658
00:34:31,510 --> 00:34:32,710
find my way here today

659
00:34:32,880 --> 00:34:33,440
is that

660
00:34:34,190 --> 00:34:36,250
I felt the calling of the Phoenix God.

661
00:34:36,719 --> 00:34:38,830
I am willing to offer
all my family's wealth.

662
00:34:38,830 --> 00:34:40,489
Have mercy on me, Sect Master.

663
00:34:40,670 --> 00:34:42,190
Please allow me into the sect.

664
00:34:42,190 --> 00:34:44,120
Give me guidance and enlighten me.

665
00:34:44,670 --> 00:34:45,510
One day,

666
00:34:46,800 --> 00:34:48,530
the people of the immortal sect

667
00:34:48,739 --> 00:34:50,179
will pay in blood.

668
00:34:50,880 --> 00:34:52,230
Blood for blood!

669
00:34:52,580 --> 00:34:53,880
Blood for blood!

670
00:34:54,190 --> 00:34:55,550
Blood for blood!

671
00:34:57,230 --> 00:34:58,030
Wang Yanqing,

672
00:34:58,920 --> 00:35:00,450
were the words you just said

673
00:35:00,960 --> 00:35:02,220
truly from your heart?

674
00:35:02,360 --> 00:35:03,820
I swear to the Phoenix God,

675
00:35:04,960 --> 00:35:07,290
everything I, Wang Yanqing, said is true.

676
00:35:07,720 --> 00:35:09,180
If there is even half a lie,

677
00:35:09,440 --> 00:35:11,230
may I incur the wrath of gods and men,

678
00:35:11,230 --> 00:35:14,160
be pierced by a sword,
and die without a whole corpse.

679
00:35:15,030 --> 00:35:17,030
Please pass your judgment, Master.

680
00:35:17,510 --> 00:35:19,030
Since that is the case,

681
00:35:19,230 --> 00:35:20,920
I will represent you today

682
00:35:21,350 --> 00:35:23,310
to pray to the Phoenix God.

683
00:35:51,550 --> 00:35:54,320
May the Phoenix God grant us guidance.

684
00:36:40,840 --> 00:36:42,400
Thank you, Phoenix God.

685
00:36:43,030 --> 00:36:45,110
Thank you for your grace, Phoenix God.

686
00:36:45,110 --> 00:36:46,970
Thank you for your mercy, Master.

687
00:36:49,630 --> 00:36:50,550
Rise.

688
00:36:52,800 --> 00:36:53,760
The Phoenix God

689
00:36:54,320 --> 00:36:56,710
has felt your devotion.

690
00:36:57,480 --> 00:36:58,140
From now on,

691
00:36:58,360 --> 00:37:00,190
we are close siblings

692
00:37:00,440 --> 00:37:01,590
of the same family.

693
00:37:02,920 --> 00:37:05,510
The Phoenix God will bless you

694
00:37:06,000 --> 00:37:08,320
and guide you when you are lost.

695
00:37:08,840 --> 00:37:10,840
All believers of the Qinghong Sect

696
00:37:11,000 --> 00:37:13,590
are united with you as one,

697
00:37:14,000 --> 00:37:16,230
sharing life and death.

698
00:37:19,360 --> 00:37:20,420
Thank you, Master.

699
00:37:22,960 --> 00:37:26,960
You said you have a deep hatred
for the immortal sect.

700
00:37:27,440 --> 00:37:28,190
Today,

701
00:37:29,110 --> 00:37:31,280
I will use the blood of the immortal sect

702
00:37:31,280 --> 00:37:32,240
to baptize

703
00:37:33,070 --> 00:37:34,760
and bless you.

704
00:37:35,360 --> 00:37:37,690
I will follow your arrangements, Master.

705
00:37:37,760 --> 00:37:38,960
Should I seize power,

706
00:37:40,190 --> 00:37:42,450
I will fight the immortal sect to the end.

707
00:37:45,840 --> 00:37:47,970
Pick a prisoner from the immortal sect

708
00:37:48,510 --> 00:37:49,710
and bring them here.

709
00:37:52,360 --> 00:37:52,840
Yes.

710
00:37:59,440 --> 00:38:00,070
Senior.

711
00:38:00,590 --> 00:38:01,320
How are you?

712
00:38:02,190 --> 00:38:02,880
I'm fine.

713
00:38:03,280 --> 00:38:03,960
It's done.

714
00:38:05,320 --> 00:38:06,110
I will quickly

715
00:38:06,110 --> 00:38:08,260
undo the Nine Breaths Technique for you.

716
00:38:08,260 --> 00:38:09,300
Adjust your breath

717
00:38:09,300 --> 00:38:10,830
and steady yourself first.

718
00:38:15,910 --> 00:38:17,310
What happened to you?

719
00:38:19,030 --> 00:38:20,690
I had to damage my own vitality

720
00:38:20,770 --> 00:38:22,770
to gather the turbid qi of dead wood.

721
00:38:27,590 --> 00:38:28,650
Someone is coming.

722
00:38:45,110 --> 00:38:47,030
Look at your short-lived face.

723
00:38:47,320 --> 00:38:48,000
You'll do.

724
00:38:49,070 --> 00:38:50,200
Don't be impulsive.

725
00:38:56,190 --> 00:38:56,960
It's okay.

726
00:38:58,230 --> 00:38:59,280
I'll go.

727
00:39:00,400 --> 00:39:02,130
If I am lucky enough to survive,

728
00:39:02,830 --> 00:39:04,270
I will kill all of you.

729
00:39:05,480 --> 00:39:06,590
If I die,

730
00:39:07,630 --> 00:39:08,890
remember to avenge me.

731
00:39:10,670 --> 00:39:11,510
Don't rush.

732
00:39:12,020 --> 00:39:13,350
It'll be your turn next.

733
00:39:14,320 --> 00:39:14,920
Let's go.

734
00:39:55,550 --> 00:39:56,080
Who is it?

735
00:40:01,950 --> 00:40:04,010
The Blessing Ceremony is held today.

736
00:40:04,410 --> 00:40:06,250
What are you doing here

737
00:40:08,070 --> 00:40:09,880
instead of tending to sect matters?

738
00:40:09,880 --> 00:40:11,480
Then what are you doing here?

739
00:40:11,510 --> 00:40:12,440
Waiting for you.

740
00:40:14,140 --> 00:40:15,600
Then you are really lucky.

741
00:40:15,960 --> 00:40:17,160
You waited and met me.

742
00:40:18,150 --> 00:40:18,730
Stop!

743
00:40:26,110 --> 00:40:27,550
Master was right.

744
00:40:27,770 --> 00:40:29,250
You really are a traitor.

745
00:40:40,110 --> 00:40:41,110
Bring him up.

746
00:40:43,810 --> 00:40:44,210
Move.

747
00:40:45,040 --> 00:40:46,040
I can walk myself.

748
00:40:58,300 --> 00:40:58,840
Kneel.

749
00:41:02,740 --> 00:41:03,740
Behave yourself.

750
00:41:03,840 --> 00:41:05,190
Look at where you are.

751
00:41:07,630 --> 00:41:08,550
Where I am?

752
00:41:09,630 --> 00:41:11,230
What a big cesspit.

753
00:41:12,110 --> 00:41:13,320
Are all of you

754
00:41:13,810 --> 00:41:15,930
lining up to use the toilet?

755
00:41:16,190 --> 00:41:16,710
Slap him.
